Ƙungiyar Turai ta Thomas Bjorn, da ke ƙoƙarin kiyaye kyautar da ta yi a Hazeltine shekaru biyu da suka gabata, ta rinjayi ƙungiyar Amurka a cikin wasan kwallon kafa na safe, ta ci wasan 3-1.
