Justin Rose, wanda ba ya shiga cikin wasan foursome na safiyar yau, ya koma Henry Stenson a cikin foursome don ya doke Dustin Johnson da Brooks Koepka a matsayin na 1 da 3 a duniya, a cikin 2&1.
