Sau biyu kawai a tarihin gasar Ryder Cup, an samu wata ƙungiya ta yi asara ta maki huɗu ta fara wasan guda ɗaya, ko da yake kawai za a iya cin nasara a wasan Fury don kiyaye kyautar.
