Girgizar ƙasa da tsunami a Indonesia
Rahotanni sun ce aƙalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu a sakamakon girgizar ƙasa da tsunami da suka afkawa birnin Palu a ƙasar Indonesia a ranar Juma'a.
Saboda rashin sadarwa, rundunar 'yan gudun hijira ta kasa samun wani bayani daga yankin Donggala, wanda ke arewacin Palau, kusa da tsakiyar girgizar kasa mai karfin 7.5.
Bayan hatsarin da ya faru a Pala, an kwashe mutane fiye da 16,000.
Ga wasu muhimman bayanai game da birnin Palu da kuma yankin Donggala a tsibirin Celebes:
Palau babban birnin Celebes Central, wani lardin da ke kusa da bakin teku a yammacin tsibirin, wanda aka kiyasta yawan mutane 379,800 a shekara ta 2017.
A lokacin da girgizar ƙasa da tsunami suka auku, birnin yana bikin cika shekaru 40 da kafuwar birnin.
Donggala wani yanki ne na gari (wani yanki ne na ƙasa da lardin) wanda ke da tsawon kilomita 300 a arewa maso yammacin tsibirin.
An kiyasta cewa a shekara ta 2017, mutane 299,200 ne suka zauna a birnin.
Babban masana'antun tattalin arzikin Celebes ta Tsakiya shine kifi da noma, wanda ya ci gaba musamman a yankin Donggala da ke bakin teku.
Wani tushen samun kudin shiga na lardin shine ma'adinai na nickel, amma suna da yawa a Morowali, a gefen tekun Celebes.
Hukumar kula da bala'i ta Indonesia ta ce a cikin shekaru 100 da suka shige, girgizar ƙasa da tsunami sun addabi Pala da Donggala sau da yawa.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami da ya auku a birnin Donggala ya kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ya lalata ɗaruruwan gidaje.
A shekara ta 1996, tsunami ya kashe mutane tara a yammacin birnin Donggali.
Indonesia tana cikin yankin Pacific mai cike da wuta, kuma hakan ya sa ta yi girgizar ƙasa sosai.
Girgizar ƙasa da tsunami mafi girma a cikin 'yan shekarun nan:
2004: Wani girgizar ƙasa mai girma da ta afkawa yankin Aceh a arewacin Sumatra a ranar 26 ga watan Disamba, ta haifar da tsunami wanda ya afkawa kasashe 14, ya kashe mutane 226,000 a tekun Tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin su a Aceh.
2005: A ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu, an yi girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi a yammacin Sumatra.
A tsibirin Nias a bakin tekun Sumatra, mutane ɗaruruwan sun mutu.
2006: A kudancin tsibirin Java, tsibirin da aka fi yawan jama'a a Indonesia, girgizar ƙasa mai karfin awo 6.8 ta afku da tsunami, wanda ya afku da gabar kudu, ya kashe kusan mutane 700.
2009: Wani girgizar ƙasa mai karfin 7.6 ta afku kusa da Padang, babban birnin West Sumatra.
Mutane fiye da 1,100 ne suka mutu a sakamakon wannan aikin.
A shekara ta 2010: Girgizar ƙasa mai karfin awo 7.5 ta afkawa tsibirin Mentawai kusa da bakin tekun Sumatra, kuma ta jawo tsunami mai tsayi har zuwa mita 10, wanda ya lalata ƙauyuka da dama kuma ya kashe mutane 300.
2016: Wani girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi ta afkawa gundumar Pidie Jaya a lardin Aceh, ta haifar da lalacewa da firgici a tsakanin mutane waɗanda har yanzu suna tuna da lalacewar da girgizar ƙasa da tsunami na 2004 suka kawo.
A wannan lokacin, babu tsunami, amma gine-gine da suka yi girgizar ƙasa sun kashe mutane fiye da 100.
2018: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi ta afkawa tsibirin Lombok, tsibirin yawon shakatawa na Indonesia, ta kashe mutane sama da 500, galibi a arewacin tsibirin.
