Turai ta yi nasara a gasar cin kofin Ryder a Paris
Ƙungiyar Turai ta lashe gasar Ryder Cup 2018, ta doke ƙungiyar Amurka ta 16.5 zuwa 10.5 a filin Le Golf National a cikin biranen Paris.
A ƙasar Turai, Amurka ta yi rashin nasara a karo na shida a jere kuma ba ta lashe kofin Ryder Cup a Turai ba tun 1993.
Turai ta sake samun kyautar ta hanyar samun maki 14.5 a karkashin jagorancin kyaftin din Denmark Thomas Bjørn, wanda ya dace da cin nasarar Amurka.
Wani dan wasan Amurka mai suna Phil Mickelson, wanda ya yi rashin nasara a yawancin gasar, ya buga kwallon daga kwando kai tsaye cikin ruwa a rami na 16 na PAR3, yana ba da wasan ga Francesco Molinari.
Mai wasan golf na Italiya Molinari ya yi haskakawa a duk zagaye kuma ya zama ɗaya daga cikin 'yan wasan hudu da suka yi nasara a 5-0-0 tun lokacin da aka fara gasar a cikin 1979 a matsayin ta yanzu.
An fitar da Jordan Spieth daga wasan Amurka da 5 & 4 daga cikin 'yan wasan Turai mafi ƙasƙanci, Thorbjørn Olesen na Denmark.
Dustin Johnson, wanda ke da matsayi mafi girma a duniya, ya yi nasara a ramin biyu kafin ya yi nasara a ramin karshe da Ingila Ian Poulter, wanda zai iya zama gasar Ryder Cup ta ƙarshe.
Dan Turai mafi yawan nasarar Ryder Cup shine Mutanen Espanya Sergio Garcia, wanda ya shiga gasar takwas kuma ya sami maki 25.5 a cikin aikinsa.
