Wannan adadi ne mai ban mamaki, kamar yadda yake ga daya daga cikin manyan 'yan wasa na kowane lokaci, wanda ya lashe manyan wasanni 14 kuma ya fi Jack Nicklaus.
A duk karshen mako, 'yan wasan Amurka sun yi fama da rashin samun mai yin wasan, sai dai Patrick Reed da Justin Thomas da Tony Finau, wadanda suka yi wasa a matakin da ya dace a gasar.
