Bayanai game da fure  a Pinellas, Manatee da Sarasota
Wani rahoto na kwanan nan na Hukumar Kula da Kifi da Dabbobin Florida ya nuna cewa a wasu sassan Tampa Bay, yawan 'yan adam da ke rayuwa a cikin teku ya ragu.
FWC ta ce an samu wasu wuraren da ake ganin an yi amfani da ruwan 'ya'yan itace a Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Charlotte da Collier, kuma hakan na nuna cewa an rage yawan ruwan 'ya'yan itace.
Ƙasar tana da nisan mil 209 daga arewacin Pinellas County zuwa kudu da Lee County.
Ana iya samun 'yan kwari a kusan mil 10 daga gabar tekun Hillsborough County, amma a wurare da yawa fiye da a makon da ya gabata.
An kuma ga furen a gundumar Pasco.
A makon da ya gabata, an lura da matsakaitan matakan plankton a gabar teku da ruwan Pinellas County, low zuwa matsakaitan a gabar teku na Hillsborough County, na halitta zuwa na sama a Manatee County, na halitta zuwa na sama a gabar teku da kuma ruwan Sarasota County, na halitta zuwa na matsakaitan a Charlotte County, na halitta zuwa na sama a gabar teku da kuma ruwa a Lee County, da kuma low a Collier County.
Ana ci gaba da samun cututtukan numfashi a Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Lee, da Collier.
Amma a makon da ya gabata, ba a samu wani a arewa maso yammacin Florida ba.
